    {
      "text": "Castrol HONDA -World Superbike Team- Superbike Racing (short: Castrol HONDA Superbike Racing) is a licensed motorcycle racing game, developed by Interactive Entertainment Ltd. The game features the Honda RVF750 RC45 and the riders Aaron Slight and Colin Edwards of the 1998 Superbike World Championship season.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Castrol Honda Superbike Racing es un videojuego de carreras con licencia de motocicleta, desarrollado por Interactive Entertainment. El juego presenta la Honda RVF750 RC45 y los pilotos Aaron Slight y Colin Edwards de la Temporada 1998 del Campeonato del Mundo de Superbikes.",
      "lang": "es",
      "source": "wikipedia_es"
    },
    {
      "text": "Castrol Honda Superbike Racing è un videogioco di motociclismo, incentrato sulla Superbike. È stato sviluppato da Sony Interactive Entertainment per PlayStation.\nNel gioco è possibile guidare l'Honda RVF-RC45 in 14 circuiti mondiali realmente esistenti.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Castrol HONDA -World Superbike Team- Superbike Racing』（略称：Castrol HONDA Superbike Racing）は、Interactive Entertainment Ltd.が開発したライセンス取得済みのバイクレースゲームです。本作では、1998年スーパーバイク世界選手権のホンダ RVF750 RC45、そしてライダーのアーロン・スライトとコリン・エドワーズが登場します。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
